---
title: Gemini Uplift Flow
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LoadSession: load_session (Google account)
    LoadSession --> Navigate: Round 1
    LoadSession --> ReuseTab: Round 2+
    Navigate --> CheckAuth
    ReuseTab --> CheckAuth
    CheckAuth --> EnsureProModel: button[aria-haspopup]
    EnsureProModel --> ComposeUplift: Round 1
    EnsureProModel --> InjectReview: Round 2+
    ComposeUplift --> InjectUplift: inbox/skills/* + template + persona
    InjectUplift --> SendUplift: .ql-editor + base64_chunked_insert
    SendUplift --> WaitAck: model-response
    WaitAck --> InjectReview: Gemini acknowledges skills
    InjectReview --> SendReview: base64_chunked_insert
    SendReview --> WaitResponse: wait_for_stable (3min max)
    WaitResponse --> Extract: model-response:last-child
    Extract --> SaveOutbox: outbox/responses/
    SaveOutbox --> HashEvidence: SHA-256 chain
    HashEvidence --> ReturnResult: {status, scores, page_id}
    ReturnResult --> [*]
